N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4230.13 - Refusal to deliver

State Regulations

Any person refusing to deliver a claimed horse shall be
suspended and his case referred to the commission. The horse is disqualified
until he is delivered to the purchaser. Notes
